export const ServicesData = [
    {
        img: "./images/sap.png",
        name: "SAP",
        p: "SAP is market leader in Enterprise Application Software and Products for Business Analysis," 
         +"with >355.000 customers in more than 180 countries. Our SAP specialised team is one of the largest"
         +"in South-East Europe. With over a decade of successful history working with big European corporations and several industries, "

    {
